{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"李青全","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-21","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny686WmLYtoTGTDEIYtMwV3SichnNPwXOGDdEkiahyFAhia0UznEr5ez4LB3aXFCJqyN7fp8Ua76icxmRMg/0","content":"为什么青年人中看电视的人数变少了？\n因为他们改玩游戏，看视频了。\n为什么看视频？\n因为看视频资源多，观看时间灵活。\n为什么资源多，观看时间灵活？\n因为可以看电视台以前播放的内容。\n为什么可以看以前的内容？\n因为资源是视频网站买来放在自己服务器上的，而不是想电视那样，观众选择少。\n\n\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4329,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490069193000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"新悦","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcKuPUVAWGIRxAVo4SkNmEc9bGP9bCibGTSef90ZbzXj36qdNpqdrRH6LOJCquviaiaicVoqk7bwsJm8RqNY3dwRkjiaC/0","content":"为什么年轻人中看电视的人数越来越少？\n因为年轻人中都喜欢用电脑看视频。\n为什么年轻人都喜欢用电脑看视频？\n因为网络视频选择更多。\n为什么网络视频选择更多？\n因为互联网的发展迅速使网络视频的种类越来越丰富。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3549,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490000313000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"怪盗KID","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoB2qC1jmV4KaqzhvooclkeCibFBic8ewSfkXfmoPlGFajpn0jSibyX3v8jO807ffG0FGF6f5FFRtdRM/0","content":"为什么年轻人中看电视的人数变少了?\n1、为什么会发生这种年轻人看电视人数变少的现象？\n   因为年轻人现在看网络视频的多了？\n2、为什么看网络视频的人多会导致年轻人看电视人少？\n   因为年轻人看网络视频多是使用手机或电脑观看。\n3、为什么年轻人使用手机或电脑观看不用电视看网络视频？\n   因为年轻人使用手机或电脑更方便观看。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4439,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489990602000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"奔出柵欄的\uD83D\uDC37","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-20","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEiapXxgq3bPw9Esgkeic2TXc0v7Sqb8bChNdNMPzymMFzVfJUWWvZH0KQQXgGfTOw42yTXDs5FuunN/0","content":"1.年轻人没有那么喜欢看电视了—为什么年轻人不喜欢看电视了？\n2.因为电视上提供的内容是受限的。不喜欢的内容偏多。年轻人更喜欢用手机和电脑来看自己喜欢的内容。时间内容可控。—为什么电视上要提供这些受限的内容呢？\n3.因为电视台的工作模式，考虑到每一个群体都有不同的针对性内容。还有传播知识和公益的义务。播放时间也都是固定的。还有从广告中收益的运营模式。—那什么样的工作模式才能保障自己运营的同时也能播放更多吸引年轻人内容呢？\n\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4393,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489975894000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"藤蔓","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoMia9Hm7ZPz616AibGDibl1nqZ0VjhkZ4ybnILsZpiaCibhv5NIENGYyiblDItqq2AXgu57jJWH9Jz3Leq/0","content":"5why分析\n\n为什么年轻中看电视的人数变少了？\n因为互联网内容，操作方式更加符合年轻人的口味。\n\n是什么内容呢？\n多元化海量内容，搜索方便且定向推送\n主动搜索的内容完全是自己感兴趣的内容\n\n是什么操作方式呢？\n手机移动端，眼镜等可穿戴，更加便携灵活\n信息传播速度更及时\n\n是什么口味呢？\n多元化。年轻人对兴趣也不像长辈那样进行压抑，甚至是统一的价值观世界观，更加多元，视野也更广。电视某种程度上顾及多数人喜好，无法满足多元化的内容。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4340,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489938885000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Aven","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-19","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoEHiaTBylWfkP5h3Gr8mVTk7y1OoguaVia4gbQH9po2STdmlDDRIh5M8Q6HKX1ZibryxePwyZWq1Onc/0","content":"1.为什么是年轻人？\n2.为什么选择看电视？\n3.为什么人数变少？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4290,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489922647000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Keep moving","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEqF6jufbDorn80rkbIhg1pDXpV90htcEkxHRGhTY88saZrWAFhcBVEQv1wBv3X8aHIsLOedWCxHj/0","content":"因为现在看手机和看电脑比较多。\n为什么相较于电视，看手机和电脑比较多？\n因为看手机和电脑选择范围更广，并且电视上的内容在手机和电脑上也可以获取，电视也不可携带。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4055,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489835274000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"逗比的逗比","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6icIK0BaTrZAQOHYicibFPDHOMGT8Krhu3zyKPUFYOiaIozGicdbOFY2fG6NnULKxGbVn5VbvOW53dSz3ia2faekCO8td/0","content":"1.出现手机，电脑等替代品2.这些替代品比电视具有可移动性，更为方便看电视3.手机看电视剧可以边看边与网友交流，电视没有这样的功能4.年轻人比老年人愿意接受较为复杂的手机电脑操作。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3432,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489831471000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Grace谷","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaELv640C7eLVwPdYLyP2jMRQblcFyjjnsPKxUneMS95dD1tQ8s3Dfh0c7THxBxcan2Jcg0o92SVV3w/0","content":"1、年轻人不看电视喜欢看什么？\n2、年轻人看什么比较多？\n3、哪些人喜欢看电视？\n4、年轻人为什么不喜欢看电视？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":4021,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489827382000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"黄小鱼","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/pEmwvrI2S6adoic3GoppNoFYKcMqwPWwwvPSNQFxmfw1h1dMGfRjpYERMGP3IelbPWYJgibxcmib3iae2Do6xNrybh5PR3f2YsNa/0","content":"为什么看电视的人越来越少？因为大部分年轻人都不看电视了\n为什么年轻人不看电视了？因为电视不好看\n为什么电视不好看？因为不能看到自己喜欢的节目\n为什么不能看到自己喜欢的节目？因为总是错过播出时间\n为什么会错过播出时间？因为那个时间段需要做其他事情。\n\n之所以看电视的人越来越少，是因为电视播放受时间限制，而大部分年轻人在这段时间有其他事情要做。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3912,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489799089000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"肖竹","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-18","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ajNVdqHZLLD59UCXXaKTUtCEG9o0icohtHzK8T6MNlTKeyIANBf0tBvzpDtzbWvYOGa2wgDvGdG6k1pCFiafpDjg/0","content":"1why.因为电视内容选择面比较窄，而手机或电脑等移动设备更方便，内容更自主；\n2why.因为群众的需求利益推动了技术的进步；\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3884,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489770270000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"肖伟","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcI0UJ2jHh6Kq32DmwKibP0G39cMNZkFbRPnBHaurqjSXWfaqlePs6lzLRWjnztia1XGwZZ0SMH9xBfQ7XU5fcopPB/0","content":"我的弱势项，问不下去为什么了。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3640,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489765893000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"石小妹要减肥","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/Q3auHgzwzM7UpoKYOmkxXFkM6IxSZq9a3GG7BVO4I4WSXLgVibjz3oODCWH06BSXrhGLw4uLicbvP0CuRrtzngQw/0","content":"为什么是年轻人的人数看电视少了？而不是老年人或者儿童？\n因为年轻人更关注新兴事物，对其他媒介的接受度更高。\n\n为什么年轻人是看电视的人数少了了，而不是看电影或电脑少了？\n因为电视相对来说是传统媒体，没有电脑的信息量大，可选择面比较窄。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3632,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489761487000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Lindsay^.^","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay30l60D2UJqsylSD79tuTZtXOCLrDMpZlyPGffb6lnImOV2529AgMMl8lHmicIn1JAT5Ejr99LSuP/0","content":"（1）年轻人为什么要看电视？\n——为了放松，休闲，娱乐，学习一些知识 \n（2）现在的电视能提供给年轻人尽可能多且快速的娱乐消遣学习资源吗？\n—— 有WIFI,有了电脑，智能手机，pad等，这些载体能比电视机更快更多，且不受时间，地点限制，提供给年轻人所需要，喜欢的娱乐消遣学习资源。\n（3）为什么现在的年轻人越来越多的要求更多更快的接受新资源，娱乐消遣学习等等各方面？\n——因为时代在进步，科学技术以及人类的思想意识都在前进，尤其年轻人更建立起了自我意识且不断接触新科技技术，他们追求探索自我，不再满足于简单和安稳，他们有需求去发现，了解，掌握世界最新鲜的事物。\n\n所以年轻人中看电视的人数变少了根本上是  世界的前进，科技的发展，人们意识的改变。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3607,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489755938000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Jill Ling","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyyZN53g2CvLEGicxZ4heLHooiaCVwibvbcw8BcDsxgL2AMj3bgU2wNX8OPexCoDeHxKxE9KicExhXd1G/0","content":"1. 为什么年轻人中看电视的人数变少了？ 因为电视节目选择少，无法满足年轻人的需求\n2。为什么网络平台使用的人越来越多呢？因为网络平台上各个种类的节目很多，满足了年轻人多样化的需求\n3。为什么网络平台能提供那么多类型的节目，而电视做不到呢？因为网络平台准入门槛低，对节目质量要求没有电视节目那么高， 普通人也可以上传自己制作的节目\n4。为什么电视节目准入门槛那么高？因为电视节目受众广泛，且要受到广电总局等政府部门的严格监管\n5。为什么节目多样化，就会更受到年轻人的欢迎？年轻人喜欢追求个性与独特性，多样化的节目能满足他们的需求。年轻人还喜欢表达自己，更低的门槛让他们也有机会上传自己的节目，满足他们的成就感。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3574,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489741317000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"\uD83D\uDC8DEileen\uD83D\uDD06","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny68J8YpCcKB10sXprR5WhPk2j0teXYnZ5ULqAicJbADLzNgHwQ2eYLdu33XR9l1s9M1sJY1J8myCzRiayYnMPa71icic/0","content":"1，为什么年轻人中看电视的人变少了\n因为有电脑可以看视频\n2，为什么有电脑可以看视频就不看电视\n因为可以根据自己的时间自主选择什么时候看，看什么视频，电视只能在固定时间看自己想看的\n3，为什么需要自助选择时间\n因为年轻人比较忙，没办法固定一个时间去看自己想看的电视节目\n4，为什么年轻人比较忙\n因为要上班赚钱养自己\n5，为什么要上班赚钱就不能看电视\n因为一天的时间是固定的，只能自己去自主安排","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3564,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489739233000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"JO","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AyibbafiaiamMCT1NibWJvqonUP8wpgyMv9VFbibW13z23eLGopaoFebhOC3eueQYWpbuP5Oz15Az5R3JY/0","content":"1.为什么年轻人中看电视的人数变少了？\n因为电视的吸引力下降了。\n\n2.为什么电视的吸引力下降了？\n因为很多被吸引到网络视频节目中去了。\n\n3.为什么网络视频节目会比电视更加吸引年轻人呢？\n因为网络视频可选资源更丰富，而且方便快捷，比较电视而言广告较少。\n\n所以，年轻人中看电视的人数变少了是因为网络视频等业态的冲击，无法在资源选择和便捷上满足青年人的需求。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3545,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489731448000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"王佳","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4AywoaJCYTv4hicL3wib7fApyhLPNJiaroIhefibZ5St8K9AWkmRhDQ3astuE22Q5cDMLXKe5anwROuryia/0","content":"1.为什么年轻人看电视的人数变少了？\n因为电视和互联网相比竞争力不强。\n2.为什么互联网竞争力更强？\n因为互联网在内容、功能、选择上比电视更丰富。\n3.为什么互联网有这些优势？\n因为它是基于技术、需求和开放而开发的系统。","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3541,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489731107000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"丫头","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/ib7IQ03GF98XjoaHgicBwkEpzDs95QValAW9uMicuTVwt7LGRUyD6sukUbZL6y2iaJDFgmHFGKtq1r6uWRta02dBqt8Wzyu3YPXW/0","content":"为什么年轻人看电视的人数变少了？\n分析如下：\n\uD83D\uDD3A年轻人群体特征\n生活节奏快\n需求多样\n碎片化时间多\n爱尝试新鲜事物\n社交性强\n而这些特征，直接影响着需求：\n1️⃣便于携带\n2️⃣充分利用碎片化时间获取信息\n3️⃣获取信息丰富\n4️⃣互动性强，体验性强\n移动互联网的快速崛起，尤其是智能手机的快速出现，满足了年轻人的以上需求\n  相比之下，电视无法满足年轻人的这些需求\n综上：年轻人看电视人数变少\n  \n\n\n\n\n","voteCount":1,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3444,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489726042000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"司徒望","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-17","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny68mdKMiazH8Pdcmpql3Kga0bp7l1EmZvfzWPwNEwOicKjunZooYtzv7iaFvqZlic9Jk8vxXVMoVyWCu3Q/0","content":"为什么年轻人看电视的少了？因为他们都玩手机去了。\n为什么年轻人都玩手机了？因为手机上的功能更能吸引他们。\n为什么手机上的内容能更吸引他们？因为移动网络能让他们与外界保持联系。\n为什么他们要与外界保持联系？因为人是群居动物，需要集体给予的安全感。\n因为群居动物需要安全感这个问题无法解决，所以要从与外界保持联系着手解决。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":3489,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1489723547000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]}],"highlightList":[],"end":false},"code":200}
